Join us for a special evening of SIP AND PAINT 2ND EDITION at Mamo'sGarden47 13thEvenueBurgersdorp lichtenburg Next to KennzyGuestHouse!This special event will take place from December 9th, 2024 at 1:00 PM until Late . Guests will have the opportunity to enjoy a variety of art activities, such as painting, drawing, and pool party. Guests can also enjoy complimentary drinks and light snacks.

Package includes :Bootle of wine,Canvas to paint go home with,Platter, paint and brush,photoshoot, 360 photobooth, pool party, good music, live band and many more
